description:
Tuntun is given two binary strings. she has to make the sum of both the binary string. She is Quite weak in coding so she needs your help to do so.

#### Input Format: 
- first line contains 1st binary string
- second line contains 2nd binary string

#### Output Format:
- Print the desired binary string.

#### Constraints:
- 1<= str.length<=10000
- 0<=str[i]<=1

#### Example:
Input:
1010
1011

Output:
10101
